The University Club

The University Club, long known for its excellent catering, offers an elegantly appointed light-filled ballroom, attentive staff, and complimentary convenient parking. Enjoy cocktails on our sun porch overlooking wooded scenery, followed by dinner and dancing in a private ballroom setting.

University Club bridal parties will receive the customized attention and superior service required to make your day a truly unforgettable experience.

Features & Location

Capacity: 300
Venue is indoors
Air conditioning available

Best for:

Ceremonies, Receptions, Cocktail Hours
